ong>;PS5 数字版&lt;/strong>;（现售价 374 美元，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation%C2%AE5-Digital -slim-PlayStation-5/dp/B0CL5KNB9M/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.link/8ju5ctjya02r0&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;，和&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FSony-PlayStation-5-PS5-Digital-Console-Slim %2F5113183757%2F&amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;沃尔玛&lt;/a>;)。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;VQcjKS&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component= &quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;索尼在 PS5 周年纪念之际带回原始 PlayStation 开机画面更新&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311112/playstation-30th-anniversary-psx-boot-sequence-ps5-update&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;索尼正在制作一款手持游戏机来与任天堂竞争Microsoft&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/25/24305337/sony-handheld-gaming-console-playstation-nintendo-microsoft&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;SteelSeries 是推出 160 美元的游戏耳机，适用于您的 Xbox、PlayStation 或PC&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253924/steelseries-arctis-gamebuds-earbuds-pc-xbox-playstation-nintendo-switch-release-date-pricing&quot; }]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;nuVvQu&quot;>;如果您已经拥有 PS5 并且正在寻找新的游戏方式，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23601368/sony-playstation-ps-vr2-review-virtual-reality&quot;>;&lt;strong>;PlayStation VR 2&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>; 目前售价 &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation-VR2-PSVR2-5/dp/B0C1Q9X8VH?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/cmLNtTk4a88&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fplaystation-vr2-horizo​​n-call-of-the-mountain -bundle%2F-%2FA-88995903&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;目标&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23600772/horizo​​n-call-of-the-mountain-sony-psvr2-review&quot;>;&lt;em >;&lt;strong>;地平线呼唤山&lt;/strong>;&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;售价 349 美元（优惠 250 美元），这可能很诱人。这款虚拟现实耳机易于设置，并提供出色的 PC 级沉浸感，尽管在发布近两年后其产品阵容仍然有限。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;qfreSG&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component =&quot;productcard:12113209&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;div id=&quot;NMNAzB&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12103973&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;fzIFVD&quot;>;不喜欢 VR？这也是购买额外控制器、游戏耳机和其他 PS5 配件的好时机。即日起至 12 月 13 日，索尼标准 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21562206/ps5-dualsense-controller-review-games-features-vibrations&quot;>;&lt;strong>;DualSense 无线控制器&lt;/strong>;&lt; /a>; 促销价低至 54 美元（折扣 21 美元），&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation-DualSenseTM-Wireless-Controller-Gaming-Console/dp/B0CQKLS4RP?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt; /a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.link/pqqy8du894kfs&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fdualsense-wireless-controller-for-playstation-5-midnight -black%2F-%2FA-83374958&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Target&lt;/a>;，而反光“Chroma”版本售价 59 美元。我们推荐的 PS5 控制器并不多于 DualSense，因为大多数第三方选项都缺乏自适应触发器和触觉引擎，而这些引擎可以增加真实的张力来反映您的游戏中动作。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id= &quot;dfK7iP&quot;>;您还可以在同一时期购买 Pulse 品牌的耳机，包括 &lt;strong>;Pulse Elite&lt;/strong>;，其价格降至历史最低价 129.99 美元（折扣 20 美元），&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/ckX7ZN0AZg2&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FPlayStation-PULSE-Elite-Wireless-Headset%2F5113175920&amp;